ATK Player.
Enable 4K HDR playback.
• Integrate newest technologies on macOS.
• Enable 4K HDR playback (HDR10 & Dolby Vision).
• Surround audio.
• Supports most of video & audio codecs.
• Download subtitle from Internet.
