HD Player.
Enjoy 4K HDR contents on iPhone, iPad & TV.
• Enable 4K HDR playback (HDR10 & Dolby Vision).
• Surround audio on tvOS.
• Supports most of video & audio codecs.
• Play videos on local network (SMB sharing).
• View on AppStore
FLAC Player+.
Enjoy lossless audio.
• 10-bands Equalizer.
• Supports 5 themes: white, dark, blue, green and purple.
• Supports 24-bit, 32-bit audio output.
• Manage your songs by playlist, album, artist, composer, genre.
• Embedded cover art and lyrics.
• View on AppStore
